{"tid":293852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦副主任譚鐵牛應高層邀考察中環街市,嘉咸街卑利街重建 倡市建局增合作","createTime":"2017-06-22T13:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T00:32:27.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74bafb05ff0eead5d8c7daea87dbb62e06215857","tid":293852,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%87%89%E9%82%80%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E8%A1%97%E5%B8%82%E4%BF%9D%E8%82%B2%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE-%E5%80%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%E5%A2%9E%E8%88%87%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%2582%25B2%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b0c80765\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%2582%25B2%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&h=0b7c9af0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%87%89%E9%82%80%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E8%A1%97%E5%B8%82%E4%BF%9D%E8%82%B2%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE-%E5%80%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%E5%A2%9E%E8%88%87%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C/</a><br />\n【關西環咩事？】市建局邀中聯辦考察中環項目　副主任譚鐵牛倡與內地增合作<br />\n2017/6/22 &mdash; 13:01<br />\n中聯辦副主任譚鐵牛近日應市區重建局邀請，考察中環街市保育活化項目和卑利街嘉咸街重建項目，了解本港保育活化和市區重建工作情況。<br />\n<br />\n中央政府駐港聯絡辦公室今日公布，其副主任譚鐵牛於本周二上午，與市建局主席蘇慶和、行政總監韋志成等高層座談交流，以及到中區考察。中聯辦網頁指，譚鐵牛對市建局推動城市更新表示讚賞與肯定，並建議更好利用科技手段提高重建項目管理水平，以及增進與內地的交流合作。<br />\n<br />\n中環街市活化項目是回應行政長官2009年施政報告內委託市建局進行活化中環街市大樓的政策綱領，作為政府保育中環的其中一項重點工作。該項目將提供約1.2萬平方米連天台及其他配套設施面積在內的總樓面面積，提供大眾化文化和零售設施。卑利街嘉咸街發展計劃則提供住宅、商業、酒店及零售用地、社區設施，以及公共休憩空間。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦網頁介紹，學者出身的譚鐵牛擁有英國帝國理工學院電子電氣工程系博士學歷，於2000至2007年，擔任中國科學院自動化研究所所長。他於去年底獲委任為中聯辦副主任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/129638157_14980904742141n_ggYWC_q92dk_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F129638157_14980904742141n_ggYWC_q92dk_1200x0.png&h=bfb08f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中聯辦副主任譚鐵牛考察中環街市保育項目　（相：中聯辦） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/129638157_14980905632571n_DSvPY_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F129638157_14980905632571n_DSvPY_1200x0.jpg&h=1c20fc90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中聯辦副主席譚鐵牛考察卑利街嘉咸街重建項目商鋪　（相：中聯辦）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市建局:中聯辦到訪屬一般交流參觀 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1591325/%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%3A%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%88%B0%E8%A8%AA%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1591325%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B1%2580%253A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2588%25AC%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25A7%2580&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=eee6a4a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1591325/%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%3A%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%88%B0%E8%A8%AA%E5%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80</a><br />\n<br />\n市建局高層陪同中聯辦副主任考察重建項目　許智峯批評 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337717-20170622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337717-20170622.htm&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bc9d7a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337717-20170622.htm&h=26ba50e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337717-20170622.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n許智峯批市建局高規格招待譚鐵牛不恰當<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1591025/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E6%89%B9%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%9A%E9%90%B5%E7%89%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%B0%E7%95%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1591025%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%259A%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%2589%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2581%25B0%25E7%2595%25B6&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=80adac4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1591025/%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E6%89%B9%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%9A%E9%90%B5%E7%89%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%B0%E7%95%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n【李八方online】市建局同中聯辦 邊個講大話？<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170622/56863200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170622%2F56863200&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDQ9